ny/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n史記 / 韓兆琦編<br />\n<img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/mORf3MhxfPO1SkA3yOukMFqMib6hg1FyIgb0ia0IBxsntfRxnnDUp8gHhTWFqY535xISCFk4PQ1MTKe835cawqbg/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FmORf3MhxfPO1SkA3yOukMFqMib6hg1FyIgb0ia0IBxsntfRxnnDUp8gHhTWFqY535xISCFk4PQ1MTKe835cawqbg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng&h=659eb653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即係簡體？<br />\n<br />\n史記 / 汪受寬新撰<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.chunghwabook.com.hk/Public//files/book//md/upload/bb5651a6-aee3-4695-9d0b-c670c135de76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chunghwabook.com.hk%2FPublic%2F%2Ffiles%2Fbook%2F%2Fmd%2Fupload%2Fbb5651a6-aee3-4695-9d0b-c670c135de76.jpg&h=4a668ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.d4j.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/20190711093602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.d4j.cn%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F20190711093602.jpg&h=b0c0fd4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即係剪輯版？<br />\n圖解史記 / 李鵬著.<br />\n史記列傳詩 / [楊俊明著].<br />\nQ版爆笑史記之帝王.神主 / 韓冬著.<br />\n流傳千年的史記故事 / 江輝著.<br />\n史記 / [司馬遷原著 ; 陳俊楓改編].<br />\n白話二十五史故事. [第 1冊], ≪史記≫卷. 1 / 韋杰, 盛佳[著].<br />\n白話二十五史故事. [第 2冊], ≪史記≫卷. 2 / 傅曉紅[著].<br />\n史記評賞 / 賴漢屏著.<br />\n一次讀完史記故事<br />\n關於史記的100個故事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢隻都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/pic2.zhimg.com/50/79b19c209e21cde6fbf0af078fce365d_hd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F50%2F79b19c209e21cde6fbf0af078fce365d_hd.png&h=e4c91e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/pic4.zhimg.com/50/cc817b7355536aa974061e79e5b70e6b_hd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fpic4.zhimg.com%2F50%2Fcc817b7355536aa974061e79e5b70e6b_hd.png&h=a7a29ee9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f715a71b1af0429841dba5707a85787300bd0e7d","tid":1849994,"uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44214f9c8aca0cdf65bb2c8c785725b38a2cd63","tid":1849994,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"檢索：意大利統一<br />\n<a href=\"https://webcat.hkpl.gov.hk/search/query?term_1=%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E7%B5%B1%E4%B8%80&amp;theme=WEB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebcat.hkpl.gov.hk%2Fsearch%2Fquery%3Fterm_1%3D%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E4%25B8%2580%26theme%3DWEB&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=9d733fd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://webcat.hkpl.gov.hk/search/query?term_1=%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E7%B5%B1%E4%B8%80&amp;theme=WEB</a><br />\n沒有符合的檢索結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e2c10d40ddfada80c9440d57c03c2f136b8df1","tid":1849994,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"平日則至下午八時，許多打工仔才剛收工<br />\n<br />\n個問題係香港人工時太長<br />\n你嘅解決方法就係叫圖書館職員延長佢地嘅工時就你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525f6d7c1caa40c2db70af73618778396a8f0299","tid":1849994,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1e2c10d40ddfada80c9440d57c03c2f136b8df1","tid":1849994,"uid":14983,"like"